- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses intersection type systems, which are commonly used in programming languages. 
- cs.TL (Type Theory) is another possible category as the paper deals with subtyping relations for types. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions the use of well-founded induction, which is a common technique in machine learning. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the least likely category as the paper does not focus on software engineering topics.
